Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明与黑暗\N在陷入一片混乱的战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.43,0:00:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了四魂之玉\N因缘际会聚在一起的伙伴们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.80,0:00:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越五百年的时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后仅存的四魂之玉碎片\N引导着各自的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.67,0:00:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代的传奇故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经被劈成两半\N奈落的分身婴儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被释放的传说中的\N妖马炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.32,0:00:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择了新的主人\N骑到自己的背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.55,0:00:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.32,0:00:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.46,0:00:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a world（暧昧的世界）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋力冲出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.94,0:00:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对忧郁的现实生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.91,0:00:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断在心中自我成长的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.85,0:01:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜的梦境及梦中残留的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.89,0:01:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断断续续提醒我“勇往直前”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.10,0:01:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破茧而出的我  及含苞待放的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.87,0:01:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就将它禁锢起来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.88,0:01:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.31,0:01:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.98,0:01:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go in and try（不顾一切的去尝试）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.35,0:01:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.42,0:01:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你天长地久永不分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.92,0:01:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need to cry（同样的哭泣）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.29,0:01:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孤独相伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show me a day fight（直接应战）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.26,0:01:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当伤心流泪的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.46,0:01:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它成为坚定不移的梦想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好好地窥视你的心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.96,0:02:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.67,0:02:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.91,0:02:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太得意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一半\N是要我怎么处理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点气息都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你复活了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.25,0:03:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活过来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.47,0:03:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第142话\N狂暴的炎蹄与战栗的白童子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么速度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本追不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.05,0:04:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  它就要跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.93,0:04:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它降落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄的主人\N想必就在那个地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.63,0:04:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个也被封印住的\N食人妖怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把他跟炎蹄一起除掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子  那个和尚死了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.37,0:05:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还知道来接主人\N真叫人疼爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们再像从前一样\N好好大闹一番吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别作梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.81,0:05:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是炼狱鬼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.61,0:05:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管我是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我滚回坟墓去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.82,0:05:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是让炎蹄甘心\N让我骑的炼狱鬼大爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.49,0:05:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然敢跟我较量\N真是好大的胆子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊  来啊来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.51,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.51,0:05:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点点而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.15,0:06:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来那匹叫作炎蹄的妖马\N真的不好对付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.79,0:06:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们人类玩的小把戏\N怎么可能对付得了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命中注定要得到这个天下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.74,0:06:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又躲开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种速度的确很难缠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  再接我一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.05,0:06:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.06,0:06:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太饿了\N都是因为太饿了才没有力气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.49,0:06:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然\N我怎么可能输给那个臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.27,0:06:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼狱鬼和炎蹄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  被他们跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把他们找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然\N他们一定会酿成大祸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼狱鬼是食人的鬼怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要快点想办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样\N先往他们飞的方向追过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近之后\N就可以闻到他们的味道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.16,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么帮我找一套新衣服来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚醒过来就使唤我为他做事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.62,0:07:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过\N这里到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从哪里冒出来的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管我是从哪冒出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.47,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先跟你说清楚\N这里所有的人都是我的猎物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.78,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.91,0:08:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嫁给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.95,0:08:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就可以得到天下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.82,0:08:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你嫁给我的话\N是绝对不会吃亏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.42,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你一点也不像是\N会得到天下的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.03,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢嘲笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.05,0:08:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄\N让她见识见识我的能耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那匹马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑  别跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是死缠烂打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧  我就陪你玩一玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.36,0:09:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你打算跟我道歉\N就求我娶你当老婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.86,0:09:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要让你后悔你招惹了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.47,0:09:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你好好的见识一下\N连炎蹄都让我征服的强大力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了\N你怎么看都不怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.52,0:09:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是什么人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点本事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼也太目中无人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的主人是我  你忘了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来它是忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.09,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙只允许自己认同的人\N骑在它的背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有强者才能当它的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是胜利者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  我是炎蹄的主人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.74,0:11:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼\N你以为他有什么力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.96,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.00,0:11:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.37,0:11:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可恶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的人是我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然被这个小鬼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.81,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说不会太大了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.55,0:12:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想早点适应这个身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼跟奈落不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.18,0:12:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算弄脏自己的手也毫不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.70,0:12:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在这里的人\N好像都遇害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炼狱鬼下的毒手吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是马蹄印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要快点找到他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.48,0:13:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄的蹄印好像朝那个方向\N然后在这里消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说是从这里飞上天的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朝着那个方向飞去的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.73,0:13:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个气味是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有邪气  有一股邪气在逼近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还敢跑来找我们\N胆子不小嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可以打中了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人意外的打招呼方式呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是炼狱鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.42,0:14:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫炼狱鬼的家伙\N已经被我收拾掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.79,0:14:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.79,0:14:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这匹炎蹄\N好像是选择我当它的新主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它认同了我强大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.67,0:14:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.31,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是为了感谢我\N解开它的封印呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说\N是你解开这匹妖马的封印的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开封印的\N应该是神乐跟婴儿才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.78,0:14:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是说\N婴儿已被大师的法力劈成两半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.59,0:14:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭那个人类\N那个臭和尚的法力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能置我于死地吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  你就是那个婴儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是白童子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.07,0:15:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错\N我也是奈落的分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白童子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又是奈落的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.84,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫白童子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.61,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你杀害僧侣和神官的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了\N窥视彼世与此世的交界处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里到底有什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.09,0:15:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也去找找看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找四魂之玉的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说四魂之玉的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  把这种事说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么必要隐瞒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手多一点比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了谢谢我\N为你们提供了这样的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.51,0:15:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子\N碎片的事好像是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我搞不懂什么此世彼世的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过\N要是碎片真在那里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.65,0:15:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己去给我找出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.76,0:16:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让他逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要逮到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.28,0:16:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要继续杀和尚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠人类的力量还是不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.95,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被劈成两半之前\N看到的心灵光景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.95,0:16:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是\N此世与彼世的交界处吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了一片\N白雾笼罩的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.13,0:16:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能再看清楚一点就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.14,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就找妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.64,0:16:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找力量强大的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.41,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.12,0:17:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近并没有发生什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  如您所看见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这十分宁静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.13,0:17:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么像马的妖怪\N还有骑在它背上的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不好意思  没能帮上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.34,0:17:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  哪里  您太客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.67,0:17:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后一直都没有\N找到什么线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那个叫\N白童子的小孩逃走之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也没有听到\N寺庙或神社被袭击的传闻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.78,0:17:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我倒是感觉到\N有种很诡异的邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还不只是一股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诡异的邪气?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.06,0:17:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每股邪气都不是很强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.26,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过感觉上\N行动好像都很躁动混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是指\N他们不是朝向同个方向移动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.27,0:17:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他们就像是迷失了一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道好香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.41,0:18:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒跟珊瑚\N差不多也该回来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.48,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  居然是奈落那边的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来告诉我们\N剩下的四魂之玉碎片的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的叫人好意外喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.32,0:18:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了这块碎片之外\N其余的就在钢牙的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及琥珀的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的\N全部都落在奈落的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.67,0:18:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们绝对不能再让奈落\N得到四魂之玉的碎片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.58,0:18:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉那家伙  跑到哪儿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.92,0:18:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在当然坐立难安了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.12,0:18:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  没有白童子的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那小子说的什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此世与彼世的交界处\N又不知道是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道没有什么线索了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线索…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这家伙干嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.02,0:19:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.87,0:19:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.39,0:19:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到什么地方溜达了\N你这笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.99,0:19:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不在的话\N不知道戈薇会变成怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.83,0:20:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个妖怪是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是犬夜叉消灭的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是一样的夸张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里夸张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋都被砍了下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个妖怪一开始出现就没有头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.79,0:20:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始出现就没有头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是一开始就没有头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊\N所以看起来才更恐怖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师所说的\N漫无目的乱撞的邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个妖怪大概是其中的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.13,0:20:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个妖怪\N应该是被谁用刀给砍了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说\N它的头是被砍下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过妖怪都是很顽强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是靠身体也可以到处行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  剩下的邪气也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  这个伤口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法还真是笨拙得可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.66,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.59,0:21:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.64,0:21:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不知道\N这个地方是我的地盘吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.77,0:21:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼到底想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.67,0:21:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.36,0:22:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.34,0:22:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.36,0:22:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.77,0:23:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come my way 这点黑暗之尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.78,0:23:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come close to me 现在灯已照亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.36,0:23:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是简简单单的陪在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.99,0:23:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是甘太
